<bibRefCitation author="Watson, J. M. &amp; Flores, A. R." box="[306,527,2064,2086]" pageId="0" pageNumber="177" pagination="19 - 23" refId="ref3487" refString="Watson, J. M. &amp; Flores, A. R. (2009) A new and rare rosulate species of Viola (Violaceae) from Argentina. Phytotaxa 2: 19 - 23. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.11646 / phytotaxa. 2.1.3" type="journal article" year="2009">
